text: Janko Tipsarević (born June 22, 1984) is a Serbian professional tennis player. Janko became pro in 2002. He was born in Belgrade, Serbia. Janko plays tennis right handed. He has a two-handed backhand. ==Sources== * ATP Profile ==Other websites== * Tipsarevic`s official website Category:1984 births Category:Living people Category:Male tennis players Category:Serbian tennis players Category:Sportspeople from Belgrade
